	   <tr><td colspan=2><br><br>Nother argument in favor of slower attack weapons:<br><br>Ixiblat Fer has become ENRAGED!<br><br>This of course being a mob disc that auto ripostes all attacks - and ususally kicks in when a high level monster gets low HP.<br><br>Higher attack speed = instant death in this situation.<br><br>I was one of the only sub 55 warriors left standing when we took Ixiblat Fer out this weekend - and my high delay is directly responsible.<br><br>So...<br><br>If I am not the MA and my aggro control is not critical - I often swop out for higher dam/delay wepaons - and in this case It seved my life.<br><br>Just was given this hammer by a guildie who - guess what - didn't practice up his 2hb skill.  Mkes me gald I did...hehe.<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br>"First, we're gonna cut it off.  Then we're gonna kill it."<br>- Gen. Colin Powell.</td></tr>
